literals: " Last December 2020, the Local Government Unit of Bayawan City through the PRAISE Committee has initiated the grant of Incentive Bonus to all qualified elective, permanent co-terminus, and casual employees. This said incentive is derived from the job performance of the employees for the past two (2) rating periods specifically from July to December 2019 and January to June 2020. Guidelines and criteria were established by the PRAISE committee based on the employees' rank in their respective departments. "

" We have gathered data on the common feedback, comments, and suggestions of random employees. To make this official, the Human Resource Management Office together with PRAISE Committee decided to run a quick survey on how it generally affects the morale and productivity of the employees and to know the impact of the employee's performance and organization as a whole. "
"Please select/enter your answers for each corresponding inputs."
" Thank you for completing the survey! "

"e. Are you satisfied with the ratings you  received from your superior?"
"f. Do you think the overall ranking is fair & objective?"

"i. Any recommendation/suggestion to further improve the system?"
